task.description:
Implement monitor_flow using Prefect 3.x decorators.

```python
@flow(name="monitor-flow", description="Factorial experiment monitor")
def monitor_flow(
    manifest_path: str,
    poll_interval: int = 30,
    max_cycles: int = 1000,
) -> MonitorSummary:
    manifest = JobManifest.from_json(Path(manifest_path))
    for cycle in range(max_cycles):
        alerts = poll_and_check(manifest)
        if manifest.all_terminal:
            return MonitorSummary(...)
        time.sleep(poll_interval)

@task(name="poll-and-check", retries=3, retry_delay_seconds=10)
def poll_and_check(manifest: JobManifest) -> list[Alert]:
    # Same logic as monitor_factorial.py main loop body
    ...
```

The flow imports detection logic from src/minivess/compute/
(same code as Phase 1). No duplication.

Deployment: Can be started via:
  prefect deployment run 'monitor-flow/factorial' \
    --params '{"manifest_path": "outputs/factorial_manifest.json"}'
